13 WHEREAS, it is most fitting and proper that the lineworkers of Georgia be recognized for
14 their effective and dedicated service to the people of the State of Georgia.
15 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
16 commend Georgia's lineworkers for their efforts in keeping the power on and protecting
17 public safety and recognize April 14, 2025, as Georgia Lineworker Appreciation Day at the
18 state capitol.
19 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
20 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the public and the
21 press.
